Enrich your business transformation with expert support

Enrich your business transformation with expert support

     * Digital transformation
     * Let's do it together
     * Products and services
     * Customer story
     * Why Orange?


   Share

   Our consulting experts embrace your business needs and are with you
   throughout the lifecycle of your solution. From the definition of your
   strategy to the management of your ecosystem, they provide support,
   expertise and experience and accompany you as your business grows and
   changes

Your digital transformation requires support and expertise

   Find the right strategy
   Digital transformation is a journey, and your organization needs a
   clear direction to follow. Your industry requires experts who
   understand your business needs. Differentiating through innovation and
   by automating processes will give your business the advantage over your
   competition.

   Choose from complex solutions
   You want open, scalable and flexible solutions without being locked in
   to any one vendor. Your solutions must be implemented rapidly, and they
   need to fit perfectly with your existing solutions. Your employees –
   the end users – have to be properly trained so that you get the most
   out of your new tools and processes.

   Manage a multi-faceted ecosystem
   You want to ensure security and a high level of performance, alongside
   continuous improvement of your ecosystem. Your role is to provide a
   higher level of quality service with a flat or decreasing budget. You
   want to reduce multi-sourcing complexity risks and align your sourcing
   capability with your strategy.

   1,000
   Our innovator DNA, embodied by our 1,000 researchers within our more
   than 15 worldwide labs and start-up incubators, enables us to customize
   business innovation through ideation, incubation and proof of concept.

Let's accelerate your projects together


   Develop the best strategy
     * Benefit from our business consultants’ expertise in digital
       transformation and key industry-specific knowledge
     * Assess your business processes and technical innovation
       opportunities at every level of your ecosystem with the help of our
       technical experts
     * With our guidance, define the best approach to dealing with your IT
       strategy

   Build the best solutions
     * Our solution consultants are certified in 37 different domains and
       are able to assess and design solutions that optimize the adoption
       of your solution
     * Our project managers ensure that your project follows Project
       Management Institute (PMI) or other world-class methodologies
     * We commit to delivering your end-to-end solution on time to comply
       with your business objectives

   Run the best ecosystem
     * We offer governance and integration services for all aspects of
       your IT ecosystem, including performance monitoring
     * Our dedicated customer service managers are responsible for the
       performance and continuous improvement of your solutions
     * With our full support, incidents or changes in your IT network can
       be easily managed
     * We provide a single support and contact point for all your products
     * Service review and decision support empower your managers


