Aurecon takes collaboration and productivity to the next level with Orange

   "The Orange consultative approach and industry-leading service
   management model, along with a resilient and optimized network, are
   well aligned with our IT strategy. We expect significant productivity
   gains through collaboration and service improvements, while providing
   world-class service to our customers."

   Sean Elwick, Head of IS, Aurecon

Our strengths and expertise at your service


   We provide operationally tested B2B2C digital advice and expertise
   based on our own B2C experience serving 250M customers worldwide.

   Our professional services are delivered by a global expert team of over
   200 worldwide experts in charge of MSI and contract execution, 500+
   business and solution consultants, 230 project managers, 330 service
   managers and 1,500 field engineers. They are based in 115 countries and
   territories across the globe.

   We also operate 5 Major Service Centers (Brazil, Egypt, France, India
   and Mauritius) and have unmatched network coverage in 220 countries and
   territories.

   We support 32 languages, the culture and political context are part of
   our local teams’ expertise, to support you effectively and assure your
   business continuity.

   Certifications:
     * Network and application performance: Blue Coat, Cisco, Citrix,
       Compuware, Ipanema, Riverbed, OPNET, etc.
